<p><span style=3D"letter-spacing: -0.3px;">A random password generator (als=
o known as a strong password generator) is a tool that generates random, un=
ique and, most importantly secure passwords. You give it guidelines and it =
creates strong, unpredictable passwords for each of your login accounts.&nb=
sp;</span></p>
<p><span style=3D"letter-spacing: -0.3px;">Managing your passwords has beco=
me more important than ever. People online who don=E2=80=99t use password m=
anagers are three times more likely to be affected by identity theft. Find =
out more <a href=3D"https://us.norton.com/blog/privacy/password-statistics"=
