<div id=3D"text-text-ae1e1b1ecf" class=3D"cmp-text   is-rtf">
    <p>A password generator creates complex, unique passwords that you can =
use for your login accounts. <a href=3D"https://us.norton.com/feature/passw=
ord-manager">Norton Password Manager</a> has a built-in password generator =
that helps you generate strong, unique passwords within the app and at the =
same time store them more securely in one encrypted place. Our Norton Passw=
ord Generator lets you select how many characters, letters, mixed case, num=
bers, and punctuation marks you want. You can generate multiple passwords a=
t a time with the same criteria plus you can also use it to generate number=
-only PINs.</p>

</div>

