<div id=3D"text-text-0747d3f909" class=3D"cmp-text   is-rtf">
    <p>It=E2=80=99s important to create different passwords for every login=
 account, and a password generator does just that. It creates complex, uniq=
ue passwords that you can use for your online accounts. You no longer need =
to think of a new password every time you sign up for something new or set =
up a new online login. Just set up our Password Manager for added security =
and peace of mind when you browse the web. Norton Password Manager has made=
 managing and creating new logins and passwords easy.</p>

</div>

