idden" role=3D"region" aria-labelledby=3D"accordion-b4fb29f1d3-item-c077c3e=
bbb-button" aria-hidden=3D"true"><div class=3D"text">



   =20





<div id=3D"text-text-c077c3ebbb" class=3D"cmp-text   is-rtf">
    <p>A strong password should follow the below rules:</p>
<ul>
<li>At least 8-12 characters long</li>
<li>Uses upper and lowercase letters</li>
<li>Includes at least one number and one symbol</li>
<li>Does not use real words found in the dictionary</li>
<li>Does not use your personal information, like a child=E2=80=99s or pet=
=E2=80=99s name</li>
<li>Is different than your other account passwords</li>
<li>You change it on a regular basis</li>
</ul>
<p><span style=3D"letter-spacing: -0.3px;">Using easy-to-guess, common pass=
words, the same password for multiple login accounts or sharing your passwo=
rds with others all risk compromising the security of your online accounts.=
&nbsp;</span></p>

</div>

